Larb

1 lb ground chicken
2 tbsp sliced shallot
2 tbsp finely chopped spring onion
1/4 c chopped mint leaves
3 tbsp roasted rice powder (khao koor)
2 tbsp ground Thai chile
3 tbsp lime juice
2-3 tbsp fish sauce

Cook chicken with 2 tbsp lime juice in a pan over moderate heat. Stir until done. Transfer cooked chicken into medium mixing bowl. Add the remaining ingredients, and mix well. Taste and season as preferred.

